		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Very Rare</em></p><p>This book contains health and nutrition tips, and its words are charged with magic. If you spend 48 hours over a period of 6 days or fewer studying the book's contents and practicing its guidelines, your Constitution increases by 2, to a maximum of 30. The manual then loses its magic but regains it in a century.</p><section><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This item includes 48 max uses for tracking hours read.</p><p>The <strong>Read</strong> activity includes a scaling value that lets you enter the amount of hours you've read. Once you hit 48 you can use the included Active Effect to increase your Constitution.</p><p>The <strong>Reset Progress</strong> activity resets your uses to 0 if you fail to complete the book within 6 days and need to start over.</p></section>",
